videos.description: Badgers RB Jonathan Taylor shakes free for an impressive 47-yd TD run, giving Wisconsin an early 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: Taylor breaks off long run for Wisconsin's first TD

videos.description: Wisconsin RB Jonathan Taylor bursts into the open field for a 30-yd TD run, extending the Badger lead to 17 before halftime.
videos.headline: Taylor finds daylight for 2nd TD of half

videos.description: Badgers QB Alex Hornibrook finds Kendric Pryor in the end zone with just seconds left in the half to put Wisconsin up 24-0.
videos.headline: Wisconsin QB caps off first half with TD strike

videos.description: Wisconsin RB Garrett Groshek breaks through tackles en route to a 43-yd TD after receiving a screen pass from QB Alex Hornibrook.
videos.headline: Badgers RB catches screen pass and slips free for TD
